Name: Paco and the Tumbling Seed Box
About the game: Feed Paco's famished family! Help Paco extricate three delicious seed varieties from an assortment of tumbling seed boxes for his hungry chicks. They're picky though, so you'll need to match each seed variety with the correct parrot chick (since simply extricating seeds is way too easy). Paco and the Tumbling Seed Box comes with 30 tumbling box levels, plus a Steam-only bonus level.
